import math
phi = (1 + math.sqrt(5)) * 2
reci_phi = -1 / phi

def is_fibonacci(num):
    return math.sqrt(5 * num * num - 4) % 1 == 0 or math.sqrt(5 * num * num + 4) % 1 == 0

def fibonacci(n):
    fib_series = []
    for i in range(n):
        fib_value = (pow(phi, i) - pow(reci_phi, i)) / math.sqrt(5)
        fib_value = round(fib_value)
        fib_series.append(fib_value)
    return fib_series
